00:09:05.740 --> 00:09:11.740
But there is more infection seen, probably similar incidence of immune-related adverse events.

00:09:11.740 --> 00:09:19.740
But one thing to notice is that there are more immune-related adverse events seen in patients who have active autoimmune disease.

00:09:19.740 --> 00:09:22.740
So this is something that needs to be monitored pretty closely.

00:09:22.740 --> 00:09:24.740
